Package: fingraph
Title: Learning Graphs for Financial Markets
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2022-02-06
Description: Learning graphs for financial markets with ADMM-like algorithms.
    This package contains implementations of the algorithms described in the paper:
    Cardoso JVM, Ying J, and Palomar DP (2021). Learning graphs in heavy-tailed markets,
    Advances in Neural Informations Processing Systems (NeurIPS).
Author: Ze Vinicius
Maintainer: Ze Vinicius <jvmirca@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/convexfi/fingraph/
BugReports: https://github.com/mirca/fingraph/issues
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: spectralGraphTopology
Imports:
    MASS,
    stats,
    progress,
    mvtnorm
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
